thread.title: Trump tariffs to kick U.S. consumers in the can

title: Trump tariffs to kick U.S. consumers in the can
text:
Trump tariffs to kick U.S. consumers in the can Thursday, May 10, 2018 - 02:10
Pacific Coast Producers is getting squeezed, thanks to President Trump's sweeping tariffs, the California farm cooperative is paying more to put fruits and vegetables into tin-coated steel cans, leaving it with little choice than to pass the cost onto consumers.
